Project #:  12 





 











Plat De Joûr – One Stop Food Application 



Project #:  12 




Members:Anish Naresh Punamiya, Akshay Jain, Sahil Jain, Viraj Paresh Shah






Description:Plat De Jour is an AI-powered food image recognition tool that takes an image as input and provides a recipe along with the ingredients and a list of restaurants that serve the food item. Our image-to-recipe generation system is built upon state-of-the-art deep learning techniques and aims to promote AI in the food and healthcare industry.





